metadata.name: Pineal wyvern
metadata.description:
The beast lays dormant, sending signals to our subconscious minds, translating them into thoughts, bringing forward our passion and sense of purpose. It's golden scales radiate with universal energies pulsating throughout our minds. Be embraced by it's healing warmth, be in awe of it's power to change the course of life itself.

Created using Blender 3D software, merging technology and my own creative flow, bringing something that wasn't, into being.
